<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Flor - Nursing jobs with transparent pay, no spam, perfect matches. Launching 2026.">
    <title>Flor - Coming 2026</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            max-width: 200px;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .logo-fallback {
            font-size: 80px;
            display: none;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .coming-soon {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            min-width: 180px;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .social-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0.9;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        
        .social-link:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .investor-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .investor-section p {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .investor-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .investor-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        
        .investor-link:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .logo img {
                max-width: 150px;
            }
            
            .logo-fallback {
                font-size: 60px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 42px;
            }
            
            .tagline {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .description {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .social-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="flor_logo.jpeg" alt="Flor Logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
            <div class="logo-fallback">🌸</div>
        </div>
        <h1>Flor</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Built for nurses, by nurses</p>
        
        <p class="description">
            Find your next nursing job with complete transparency.<br>
            Real pay ranges. No recruiter spam. Direct connections.
        </p>
        
        <div class="coming-soon">🚀 Launching 2026</div>
        
        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="for_nurses.html" class="cta-button">For Nurses</a>
            <a href="https://employersurvey.tiiny.site" class="cta-button" target="_blank">For Employers</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/florfornurses" target="_blank" class="social-link">📸 Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@florfornurses" target="_blank" class="social-link">🎵 TikTok</a>
            <a href="mailto:hello@florfornurses.com" class="social-link">✉️ Email</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="investor-section">
            <p>Investor Inquiries</p>
            <div class="investor-links">
                <a href="https://tr.ee/lzJv5JtKmU" target="_blank" class="investor-link">View Pitch Deck</a>
                <a href="https://appendix.tiiny.site" target="_blank" class="investor-link">View Appendix</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
